biological daughter.Police spokesperson Colonel Moetshe Ngoepe said it is
alleged that the suspect and his wife got separated and there was an agreement
that they will have a shared parenting custody of their two children - a boy
and a girl.Ngoepe said that last week, the suspect took these kids
